flowchart TB
    User[Business User / Admin] -->|HTTPS| App[Azure App Service]
    App --> Insights[Application Insights]
    App --> KV[Azure Key Vault]
    App --> Storage[Storage Account / Private Blob Container]
    RG[Resource Group] --> VNet[Azure Virtual Network]
    VNet --> Subnet[Application Subnet]
    Subnet --> NSG[Network Security Group]
    NSG --> App
    Insights --> LAW[Log Analytics Workspace]
    Monitor[Azure Monitor] --> Alert[Metric Alert Rule]
    LAW --> Alert
    Alert --> Ops[Cloud Operations Response]
